<rss version="2.0"><channel><title>Pablo Iranzo Gómez's blog - golang</title><link>https://iranzo.io/</link><description>A bunch of unrelated data</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2020 11:44:24 +0200</lastBuildDate><item><title>Go (golang) plugin in Citellus</title><link>https://iranzo.io/blog/2020/06/14/go-golang-plugin-in-citellus/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;I wanted to practice a bit Go programing, so I divided that task in two parts, one, adding a golang extension for Citellus and a sample, but working plugin using&amp;nbsp;it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If interested in the code it&amp;#8217;s available at the review at &lt;a href="https://review.gerrithub.io/c/citellusorg/citellus/+/495622"&gt;https://review.gerrithub.io/c/citellusorg/citellus/+/495622&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
